#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:booking_engine.booking_engine_product_attribute_view_form
msgid "When set, enables to capture the number of guests per attribute value."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ຈະສາມາດບັນທຶກຈຳນວນແຂກຕໍ່ຄ່າຄຸນລັກສະນະໄດ້."

#. module: booking_engine
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:booking_engine.x_has_checkout_cleaning_field_planning_role
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:booking_engine.x_has_checkout_cleaning_field_product_template
msgid ""
"When set, on a daily basis, check-out house keeping tasks are created for "
"resources in due out occupancy."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ວຽກແມ່ບ້ານຫຼັງແຈ້ງອອກຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນທຸກມື້ ສຳລັບຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ຮອດກຳນົດອອກ."

#. module: booking_engine
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:booking_engine._x_has_stayover_cleaning_field_planning_role
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:booking_engine._x_has_stayover_cleaning_field_product_template
msgid ""
"When set, on a daily basis, stay-over house keeping tasks are created for "
"resources in stay-over occupancy."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ວຽກແມ່ບ້ານລະຫວ່າງເຂົ້າພັກຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນທຸກມື້ ສຳລັບຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ຍັງພັກຢູ່."

#. module: booking_engine
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:booking_engine.x_is_customer_satisfaction_survey_field
msgid ""
"When set, the survey email will be sent automatically to rental order "
"customers.\n"
"Note that saving a new survey with this set will archive previous survey "
"with this setting to become the default satisfaction survey."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ອີເມວແບບສອບຖາມຈະຖືກສົ່ງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ.\n"
"ໝາຍເຫດ: ການບັນທຶກແບບສອບຖາມໃໝ່ດ້ວຍຄ່ານີ້ ຈະເກັບມ້ຽນແບບສອບຖາມເກົ່າ ແລະ "
"ໃຊ້ອັນນີ້ເປັນແບບສອບຖາມຫຼັກແທນ."

#. module: booking_engine
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:booking_engine.x_is_house_keeping_project_field_project_project
msgid ""
"When set, the tasks from this project are used for house keeping management "
"in the accommodation app."
msgstr "ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າ, ວຽກຈາກໂຄງການນີ້ຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້ເພື່ອຈັດການວຽກແມ່ບ້ານໃນແອັບທີ່ພັກ."

#. module: booking_engine
